name: BOOM BOX GOLD BRACELET
description: Crafted in 14 karat white or yellow gold, this bold bracelet features hand-set round brilliant diamonds along the face for maximum sparkle. The gold purity may be ordered in 14k or 18k depending on your preference; 24 karat is available on request for a richer colour. Each stone is carefully set by hand. A modern, everyday piece that can be customised for wrist size and gold tone. Chain and clasp are included in matching gold.

name: FUTURE KING PENDANT
description: This striking pendant is made in solid gold; we offer it in 14 karat or 18 karat yellow, white, or rose gold. The design is set with brilliant-cut diamonds and accents of emerald and onyx for contrast. The centre can be ordered with different gem combinations. Chain length and gold colour are specified at the time of order. A contemporary silhouette that works as a statement piece for both men and women.

name: Walking Lion Diamond Pendant 14k Solid Gold
description: Fully sculpted walking lion in 14 karat solid gold with pavé-set round brilliant diamonds across the mane, body, and face. Also available in 18k or 22k gold for a deeper hue. Each diamond is hand-set for lasting hold. The pendant is supplied with a matching gold chain; length and clasp style can be customised. A bold statement piece suitable for special occasions or daily wear.

name: Pulsera LOVE, tamaño mediano, 4 diamantes
description: Classic bangle in 18 karat gold with four round brilliant diamonds set in a secure bezel. Offered in yellow, white, or rose gold; 14k is available for a lower price point. The diamonds are selected for clarity and brilliance. Medium size; we will confirm exact inner diameter and fit when you order. A timeless piece that can be worn alone or stacked.

name: SPARTAN GOLD BRACELET
description: Heavy, masculine bracelet in solid gold with a textured, armour-like finish. Available in 14 karat or 18 karat yellow, white, or rose gold; 24 karat can be made to order for a softer, deeper colour. No gemstones; the focus is on the weight and finish of the gold. Wrist size and clasp style are customised. Ideal for everyday or occasion wear.

name: RTM 21
description: Elegant ring with a clean, modern profile. The band is crafted in 14k or 18k gold—yellow, white, or rose—and can be set with a centre stone (diamond or coloured gem) or left as plain gold. Ring size and gold karat are confirmed when you order. A versatile design suitable for engagement, wedding, or daily wear.
